--- Important Notes ---
1. TIME SYNC: Device clock must be accurate within 30 seconds.
   Enable "Set Automatically" in your device's date/time settings.

2. DO NOT run other VPN protocols (OpenVPN, WireGuard, etc.) on this
   server. They will get the IP flagged and blocked.

3. TO UPDATE: cd /opt/3x-ui && docker compose pull && docker compose up -d

{% if domain_mode | bool %}
4. CLOUDFLARE SETUP (required for CDN fallback):
   - Add your domain in Cloudflare dashboard
   - Create an A record pointing to {{ server_public_ip }}
   - Enable the orange cloud icon (Proxy)
   - Set SSL/TLS mode to "Full (Strict)"
   - In Network settings, enable WebSockets

{% endif %}
5. IF CONNECTION STOPS WORKING:
   - Try the CDN fallback configuration
   - Get a new server IP from your hosting provider
   - Re-run the Ansible playbook with the new IP

6. SNI TARGET: Currently using {{ reality_sni }}.
   Alternatives: www.twitch.tv, dl.google.com, github.com
   Use RealiTLScanner to find optimal targets near your server.

